Fragment Type: Opening Story — The Voice That Begins the Line  
Steward: John Carroll  
Status: Active — to be read before all other fragments

---

1. This Is Where Our Line Begins Again
Every family has a story.  
Some stories are heavy.  
Some stories are loud.  
Some stories are lost before they’re ever told.

This one is different.

This is the story of a line that chose to start over —  
not by forgetting the past,  
but by refusing to pass down its weight.

This is where our line begins again.

---

2. I Walked Far So You Could Start Close
I didn’t build this Codex from theory.  
I built it from:

- mistakes  
- lessons  
- late nights  
- hard truths  
- quiet victories  
- lived experience  

I walked farther than I needed to  
so you wouldn’t have to start where I did.

You begin closer to clarity than I ever was.

---

3. You Don’t Owe Me My Journey
You don’t owe me:

- my battles  
- my regrets  
- my survival  
- my scars  

You don’t owe me a repeat of my life.

You owe yourself the chance to live yours cleanly.

That is the whole point of this Codex.

---

4. What I Give You Is Not Weight — It’s Direction
I’m not handing you a burden.  
I’m handing you:

- grounding  
- understanding  
- emotional steadiness  
- a starting point I never had  

This Codex is not a command.  
It’s a compass.

You choose the path.

---

5. You Are Free to Become Yourself
You are not required to:

- be like me  
- think like me  
- walk like me  
- carry what I carried  

You are free to become yourself  
with more clarity than I ever had at your age.

That is the gift.  
That is the point.  
That is the promise.

---

6. When You Read This, Know I Was Thinking of You
I didn’t write this for the world.  
I wrote it for:

- my son  
- my grandson  
- the ones who come after  
- the ones who deserve a clean start  

When you read this,  
know that I was thinking of you  
long before you ever opened these pages.

---

7. Signature Line
This Codex is not the story of where I came from.  
It is the story of where you begin.

Walk forward with clarity.  
Walk forward with intention.  
Walk forward knowing the line behind you stands clean.

— Codex.LineagePrologue.v001

